Title: Non-diagonal solutions to reflection equations in $su(n)$ spin chains
Authors: J. Abad and M.Rios
Comments: 9 pages, PlainTex , two figures uuencoded, Harvmac.
Report-no: DFTUZ 95-05
Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B352 (1995) 92-95
\\
The reflection equations in a $su(3)$ spin chain with open boundary conditions
are analyzed. We find non diagonal solutions to the boundary matrices. The
corresponding hamiltonian is given. The solutions are generalized to $su(n)$.
